FUTURA LABORATORIES

FUTURA LABORATORIES is a design company and lifestyle brand created by the artist FUTURA2000 in 1997, as a spinoff group to the parent company at that time; PROJECT DRAGON. FUTURA LABORATORIES has always worked closely with UMBRELLA FILMS for visual amplification and TARANTULA DESIGNS as a graphic think tank. The brand has created many collections over multiple decades and found numerous partners in various collaborative efforts. FUTURA LABORATORIES was rebooted in 2019 with excitement and engagement across multiple platforms.
